race.comment: One for the stayers. MR BUSTER (1) has hit a purple patch of form stringing three wins together on the bounce with Maloney being in the saddle for two of those victories. Looks ready for the extra furlong now and can add to the picket fence. The well-related CAVALRY MAN (2) (half to G2 winner Positive Peace) is a consistent conveyance who has hit the top-five at his past nine outings. Gets 2kg weight relief from the low draw and can make his presence felt. WOWZINO (7) loves it here on his home circuit with two wins and a second from just three spins. Drawn to get all the favours from the inside alley and rates a genuine top-three prospect. KALUAKOI (6) has been thereabouts at the past four efforts and looks to be building up to another win. In the mix. COUNTER (4) best of the rest in a race with only a handful of chances.
